## Tokens — single source of truth

| Token | File |
|---|---|
| Colors | `app/globals.css` (CSS variables) |
| Tailwind theme | `tailwind.config.ts` |
| Spacing | `tailwind.config.ts` `theme.spacing` |
| Type | `tailwind.config.ts` `theme.fontSize` + `fontFamily` |
| Radius | `tailwind.config.ts` `theme.borderRadius` |
| Shadow | `tailwind.config.ts` `theme.boxShadow` |
| Motion | `tailwind.config.ts` `theme.transitionDuration` + `transitionTimingFunction` |

**NEVER use values outside these tokens.** No `mt-[13px]`, no inline `#3a4f6b`, no one-off radii.

